font-family: 宋体;"></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei"; font-size: 16px;">即球腔的等效刚体缩为一个质点。上述结论不难从物理观点作出解释：由于理想流体不存在黏性摩擦力，当主刚体绕腔体的对称轴旋转时，腔壁的法向约束力均指向对称轴，不可能带动原来静止的液体<span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei"; text-align: justify;">绕对称轴</span>旋转，<span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei"; text-align: justify;">等效刚体</span>绕对称轴的惯性矩必等于零。球腔的腔壁的法向约束力均指向球心，刚体绕任何轴旋转均不可能带动腔内液体的运动。将盛满水的脸盆<span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei"; text-align: justify;">缓慢转动，观察盆内的水能否保持平衡就是</span>最简单的实验。</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><br></p><p style="margin-left:28px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei"; font-size: 16px;"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei"; line-height: 150%;">2</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei"; line-height: 150%;">．</span></strong><strong> </strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei"; line-height: 150%;">流体粘性与边界层理论</span></strong></span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;"></span><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">  </span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, "Microsoft YaHei"; font-size: 16px;">在实践中观察，上述球腔内流体的运动并非完全不受刚体运动的影响。原因是任何流体不可能绝对无粘性。对理想流体的分析结论不可能完全符合实际情况。要使理论分析更符合实际情况，必须考虑粘性的作用。<br></span></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size:14px;font-family:宋体">  </span><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";">考虑液体粘性的 Navier-Stokes 方程的数学求解非常困难。为此必须想出更容易处理的方法。德国力学大师普朗特 (Prandtl,L.) 提出了一个很重要的概念，即<strong>边界层</strong>理论（图 2）。这个理论认为，对于粘性较小的一般情况，粘性对流体运动的影响仅局限在与腔壁接触的薄边界层以内。边界层以外流体的运动仍可视为理想流体。因此 Rhukovsky 等效刚体理论仍可利用，但仅限于边界层以外区域内的流体。</span><br></p><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt width="332" height="401" style="width: 332px; height: 401px;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"></span></p><p style="text-align:center;text-indent:29px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family:宋体">图</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">2  </span><span style="font-family: 宋体">普朗特</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif">(Prandtl,L., 1875-1953)</span></p><p style="text-indent: 29px; line-height: 150%;"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif"><br></span></p><p style="text-indent: 29px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";"><span style="font-size: 16px;">依据边界层理论，边界层的厚度 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>δ </em></span>与运动粘性系数 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>ν = μ/ρ</em></span><em> </em>的平方根成比例。<span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>μ</em>, <em>ρ </em></span>分别为流体的粘性系数和密度（具体分析可参阅文末的附录）。以一元流动的最简单情形为例，设平板朝 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>x</em></span><em> </em>轴方向以速度 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><strong><em>v </em></strong></span>运动，流体<span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;">沿 </span><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; white-space: normal;">x </em><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; white-space: normal;"></em><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;">轴<span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;">的流速为 </span><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; font-size: 20px;"><strong style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; white-space: normal;"><em>u</em></strong></span>。</span>平板对流体作用的粘性切应力 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><strong><em>τ </em></strong></span>沿 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><strong style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; white-space: normal;"><em>v -u</em></strong></span><strong style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; white-space: normal;"><em> </em></strong><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;">方向，</span>与边界层内流速变化的梯度 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;">(<em>v - u</em>)/<em>δ </em></span>成正比 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;">（图 3）</span>：</span><span style="font-size: 14px;"></span></span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman',serif"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";">                                                         <img src="https://cors.zfour.workers.dev/?http://image.sciencenet.cn/home/202111/19/145212ruh0nnd6lhdc6hy6.png" title alt="粘性10.png" width="182" height="80" style="width: 182px; height: 80px;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">                                                                      (11)<br></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"><br></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt width="396" height="230" style="width: 396px; height: 230px;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";">图3  <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;">边界层内的流速梯度</span></span></p><p><span style="font-size: 16px; font-family: "times new roman";"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-family:times new roman"></span></p><p style="line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";">       <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;">要分析此粘性切应力如何影响流体的运动，就不能将腔内流体视为理想流体。若为离散化起见，将腔内的流体团视为不变形的刚体，则由于腔壁的限制，只有球形腔内的流体是唯一不受腔壁约束的特例。将球腔内的流体 “固化” 成刚性球体后，其在腔内的转动不受腔壁的约束。如忽略<span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 24px;">边界层</span><span style="font-family: "times new roman";">粘性力的存在，球形流体团在腔内的旋转就与主刚体的运动完全解耦，不能正确反映充液刚体的实际情况。要反映<span style="font-family: "times new roman";">主刚体与腔内流体之间的耦合作用，必须考虑<span style="font-family: "times new roman"; line-height: 24px;">边界层的</span><span style="font-family: "times new roman";">粘性力对刚体球运动的影响</span></span></span>。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 29px; line-height: 150%; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;">以半径为 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>R</em></span><em> </em>的球腔中心 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>O</em></span><em> </em>为原点，建立已固化为刚体的流体团坐标系<span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"> (<em>O-xyz</em>)</span>，球面上任意点 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>P</em></span><em> </em>相对 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>O</em></span><em> </em>的矢径为 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><strong><em>R</em></strong></span>，<em><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; white-space: normal;">P </em></em>点的位置以球坐标 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;">(<em>R,θ,ϕ</em>)表</span>示（图 4），则在 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>P </em></span>点处的微元面积 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;">d<em>σ = R</em>sin<em>θ</em>d<em>θ</em>d<em>ϕ </em></span>內腔壁作用的粘性切向力为<span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"> <strong><em>τ</em></strong>d<em>σ</em></span>，对 <em><em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; white-space: normal;">O</em> </em>点构成粘性摩擦力矩 <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px;"><em>M</em><sub>d</sub></span><sub> </sub>：</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:times new roman"></span>                           <img src="https://cors.zfour.workers.dev/?http://image.sciencenet.cn/home/202111/19/151328o72j0u2jjh6b9y63.png" title alt="粘性11.png" width="398" height="60" style="width: 398px; height: 60px;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">                                  (12)<br></p><p><br></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt width="322" height="303" style="width: 322px; height: 303px;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></p><p style="text-align: center;">图4   <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;">流体团的球坐标</span></p><p><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;"><br></span></p><p><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px;"></span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;">于是充液腔刚体的运动被离散化为主刚体和刚体球组成的双刚体系统，刚体之间藉粘性摩擦力矩 <em style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 20px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; white-space: normal;">M</em><sub style="font-family: "times new roman"; text-align: justify; text-indent: 29px; white-space: normal;">d</sub><sub> </sub>维持联系。可利用离散系统的传统方法建模和求解。</span></p><p style="line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: "times new roman";">     <span style="font-family: "times new roman"; font-size: 16px;"> 以上分析仅限于球形腔特例。关于一般形状腔内的有旋流动将在另文中叙述。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:70px;line-height:150%"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: "times new roman";"><br></span></p><p style="text-indent:70px;line-height:150%"><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: "times new roman";"></span></p><p style="text-align:center;text-indent:29px;line-height:150%"><span style="font-size: 24px;"><strong><span style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 宋体;">附录：关于边界层的厚度和流速分布的分析</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:70px;line-height:150%"><span style="line-height: 150%;
